{"tid":956063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醒醒吧！人家有妹妹　6歲的他還兄妹結婚","createTime":"2018-12-26T03:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T21:10:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a55a664b1953b980649d55624bab8452b015925","tid":956063,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"泰國一對6歲龍鳳胎、哥哥吉他(Guitar)和妹妹奇葳(Kiwi)，兩人上周一在曼谷完成婚禮，婚禮不僅隆重盛大，龍鳳胎的父母及親朋好友都相當開心，因為他們相信，吉他和奇葳在前世是對感情甜蜜的戀人，愛到生死相許，因此轉世到這輩子成為龍鳳胎兄妹。<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，在泰國部分地區相信著一種傳說，那就是龍鳳胎的前世是戀人轉世，曾經愛到生死相許，因此這輩子投胎，以龍鳳胎兄妹的形式降臨人世間。吉他與奇葳的父母、31歲的爸爸馬里拉特(Amornsan Sunthorn Malirat)和30歲媽媽法查拉蓬(Phacharaporn)都認為，只要吉他和奇葳的年紀一到，兩人越早「結婚」越好，也能為他們未來的人生帶來幸福與運氣。<br />\n吉他和奇葳的婚禮可不馬虎，一樣有彩禮，包括20萬泰銖(約新台幣18萬元)的聘金，和價值約新台幣4萬元的金飾，現場親朋好友聚齊一堂，為這對龍鳳胎兄妹的「婚姻」慶祝。不過法查拉蓬也說，這個「龍鳳胎婚禮」的主要目的，是讓孩子們能更順利成長，兩人一輩子的親情不會斷，但等到兩人成年後，就能各自找對象結婚。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ewid19u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwid19u.png&h=9e5becde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBcFG9u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBcFG9u.png&h=7d443c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQgvjWa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQgvjWa.png&h=f0f7f557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181226/1489900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181226%2F1489900&d=Fnn%2Flz3z3YGUq6w1LWtuEhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=cbb65577\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181226%2F1489900&h=f98d8e05\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181226/1489900</a>"},{"pid":"e1c160716372268758abddd9a762b12c90cdc447","tid":956063,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cab72189b8fe47213af8f8cec4caff6a4cd7d82","tid":956063,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccc7d7dfb55c1baf35d476524c78d2441b440065","tid":956063,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T18:15:05.000Z","msg":"因為他們相信，吉他和奇葳在前世是對感情甜蜜的戀人，愛到生死相許，因此轉世到這輩子成為龍鳳胎兄妹<br />\n<br />\n有情人終成兄妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783b95ca48407e89d3854843986771027263b208","tid":956063,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T21:10:43.000Z","msg":"德國骨科"}]}